Package org.goplanit.utils.zoning

Interface TransferZoneGroup

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable, Comparable<IdAble>, ExternalIdAble, IdAble, Iterable<TransferZone>, ManagedId
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TransferZoneGroupImpl
    public interface TransferZoneGroup
extends ExternalIdAble, ManagedId, Iterable<TransferZone>
    A group of transfer zones, can be used to represent for example train stations.

    markr
